    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "You can write <code>val randomNumber = (min..max).random()</code> where <code>min</code> and <code>max</code> are the edges of the specified range. Refer <a href=\"https://kotlinandroid.org/kotlin/kotlin-generate-a-random-number-in-specific-range/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Kotlin – Generate a Random Number in specific Range</a>"
